05:51.151 --> 05:52.516
Hey. Hey, Al? Al?

05:52.619 --> 05:54.246
You want something?

05:54.354 --> 05:56.823
Big biz. Big biz. Big biz.

05:56.923 --> 05:59.255
Big, big, big biz.

05:59.359 --> 06:01.487
Yeah, Al.
Uh, how'd your meeting go?

06:01.595 --> 06:03.290
