That's nice, Al.

07:04.357 --> 07:05.381
Hello.

07:05.492 --> 07:07.654
Yeah. Uh-huh.

07:07.761 --> 07:09.559
Fonz, it's for you.

07:09.663 --> 07:11.995
Go get her, Fonz.

07:12.098 --> 07:14.362
It's the overseas operator.

07:15.969 --> 07:17.960
Yo.

07:19.205 --> 07:20.263
What?

07:20.373 --> 07:21.568
All right, all right, all right.

07:21.675 --> 07:23.006
Calm down. Calm down.

07:23.109 --> 07:24.804
Here we go.

07:24.911 --> 07:27.505
