a cherry fizz.

11:01.895 --> 11:03.329
That strong, huh?

11:03.429 --> 11:05.193
Well, maybe you
better forget it.

11:05.298 --> 11:07.096
Partners, huh, A.D.?

11:07.200 --> 11:09.168
Yeah, partners.

11:09.269 --> 11:10.430
Well, not yet.

11:10.537 --> 11:12.505
