a big decision like that,

11:12.605 --> 11:14.972
I think we ought to consult
with an accountant,

11:15.074 --> 11:16.303
-a lawyer.
- A lawyer?

11:16.409 --> 11:18.173
Yeah, because a partnership,

11:18.278 --> 11:20.542
there's a lot of things
to be considered.

11:20.647 --> 11:22.445
I totally agree with you.

11:22.549 --> 11:24.984
And here's something
you should consider right away.

11:25.084 --> 11:26.609
Boys!

11:32.392 --> 11:34.019
That's Leo...

11:34.127 --> 11:36.186
Oh, hi, Leo.

11:37.997 --> 11:39.522
And that's the Claw.

11:41.568 --> 11:43.058
Claw?

11:43.169 --> 11:44.830
You want lawyers, huh?

11:44.938 --> 11:46.838
Show 'em, Claw.

11:58.351 --> 12:00.115
The Claw.

12:00.220 --> 12:02.348
No lawyers.

12:09.028 --> 12:11.326
