23:55.534 --> 23:58.299
Hey, Mrs. C., we had
everything under control.

23:58.404 --> 24:00.429
Oh, Mrs. C.,
I wish you could have seen me.

24:00.539 --> 24:02.974
I slapped that head guy
right in the face.

24:03.075 --> 24:05.134
Well, you still should have
gone to the police first.

24:05.244 --> 24:07.372
We couldn't.
They didn't break any laws.

24:07.479 --> 24:09.641
Yeah, but if you had gone,
you would have found out

24:09.748 --> 24:11.580
that they were wanted
in three other states.

24:11.684 --> 24:13.277
I slapped a tri-state hood?

24:14.453 --> 24:15.784
I must have been delirious.

24:15.888 --> 24:17.151
I still think it was wrong

24:17.256 --> 24:18.849
