in your own hands.

24:18.958 --> 24:19.891
Please, Howard.

24:19.992 --> 24:22.290
I mean, the boys did it for me.

24:22.394 --> 24:24.988
When I first took over Arnold's
and I met all you people

24:25.097 --> 24:27.122
